title: War of the Roses: Signed "Ben Dover"
description: Laurel was using her boyfriend, Matt's phone the other day, with his permission, when a memory folder popped up from a few months ago and she found lingerie pictures of his girl best friend in it.  Matt says he was just helping his friend pick out photos to give to her boyfriend but Laurel doesn't believe him.
